filament_end_gcode:
; Filament-specific end gcode 
{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0 {endif}
filament_start_gcode:
; Filament gcode
;M412 D10  ;10mm distance
;M412 S1   ; Enable runout
;M900 K0.10 ; Linear advance spring constant -guess

{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*HOTEND_AFTERBURNER_E3D.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.02{endif}  ; 29-19-23
{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*HOTEND_AFTERBURNER_E3D.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.25} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.1275{endif}  ; guess
{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*HOTEND_SWITCH_E3D.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.38{endif}  ; guess
name: AMAZD
